      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_863A8190-22F3-0135-9824-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>View the conference.</p>
<p>Learn how to <a href="/t5/Student-Guide/How-do-I-use-the-Conferences-interface-as-a-participant/ta-p/342" target="_blank">use the Conferences interface</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
